OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has won the Makerfield by-
OL,8,Felection, increasing Labour's vote
OL,9,Fshare by 9.61%.
OL,11,FThe former Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,12,Fdefeated Reform UK's Robert Kenyon by
OL,13,F9,231 votes, gaining 5,399 more votes
OL,14,Ffor Labour than 2024.
OL,16,FHis victory now sets up a potential
OL,17,Fleadership showdown with Sir Keir
OL,18,FStarmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
