OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,FIn his speech at the count, Burnham
OL,8,Fsaid Labour now has a "final chance to
OL,9,Fchange" and "must act upon it".
OL,11,FRead Burnham's speech in full below.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"Everyone knows that politics isn't
OL,19,Fworking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
