OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"Everyone can feel that the country
OL,8,Fisn't where it should be. Tonight
OL,9,Fcould, just could, be the turning
OL,10,Fpoint.
OL,12,F"From here on I will give everything I
OL,13,Fhave got to make it so. To ensure the
OL,14,Fname Makerfield is forever synonymous
OL,15,Fwith bringing about the change this
OL,16,Fcountry needs, bringing back something
OL,17,Fwe've lost ` hope ` hope for the
OL,18,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"I am proud that this place has shone
OL,8,Fin the world's spotlight for the last
OL,9,Ffew weeks and the warmth, humour and
OL,10,Fhospitality of its people has been on
OL,11,Fshow for all to see. It will never be
OL,12,Fa stepping stone to me, but instead
OL,13,Fwill be my touchstone.
OL,15,F"A Makerfield test at the heart of
OL,16,FBritish politics will make sure that
OL,17,Fthe places Westminster has neglected
OL,18,Fwill now get fairness.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"I spoke in the campaign about the
OL,8,Fneed to change politics. I promised to
OL,9,Flead by example, from the front, as
OL,10,Fyour member of parliament.
OL,12,F"I know people who traditionally vote
OL,13,Ffor the Conservatives, the Liberal
OL,14,FDemocrats, the Greens, and perhaps
OL,15,Fmore recently for Reform UK, have
OL,16,Fgiven me their support in this
OL,17,Felection.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"I will always have respect to them
OL,8,Ffor that. And out of respect for them,
OL,9,FI will always take a place-first,
OL,10,Frather than a party-first, approach
OL,11,Fand I will focus on problem-solving
OL,12,Frather than point-scoring.
OL,14,F"And I will work hard after this by-
OL,15,Felection to heal the divisions of this
OL,16,Fcampaign. And let it be really
OL,17,Funderstood that I will be your MP,
OL,18,Fhowever you voted.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"When this borough went to the polls
OL,8,Fin May, it made a loud cry for change.
OL,9,FIn this campaign we have begun to
OL,10,Fanswer that.
OL,12,F"But I do say to my own party: this is
OL,13,Fa final chance to change. This is what
OL,14,Fpeople said directly to me on the
OL,15,Fhundreds of doorsteps that I stood on.
OL,16,FWe must hear it, we must act upon it
OL,17,Fand we must get it right. There will
OL,18,Fbe no second chance.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"But there is a chance now from this
OL,8,Fresult tonight to build a new politics
OL,9,Fbased on unity and hope. Turning away
OL,10,Ffrom the path that takes us to a
OL,11,Fdivided, dark politics of the kind we
OL,12,Fsee in the United States.
OL,14,F"We must now take this path and put
OL,15,Fthis country back on the right path,
OL,16,Fand bring people back together and get
OL,17,Fthings working properly again.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
