OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"It is with some sadness that this
OL,8,Fresult brings an end to my wonderful
OL,9,Fnine years as mayor of Greater
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,F"This city region has given so much to
OL,13,Fme. And it is a wrench to leave the
OL,14,Fjob I love. But I am not leaving the
OL,15,Fservice of Greater Manchester.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
