PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"I've always been clear that it can't
OL,8,Fachieve everything it should be and we
OL,9,Fcan't close the north-south divide,
OL,10,Fand we can't make all the great
OL,11,FEnglish cities be what they should be
OL,12,Fwithout big change at the national
OL,13,Flevel.
OL,15,F"I always knew one day I would seek to
OL,16,Fgo back to Westminster to complete
OL,17,Fthat unfinished business so that
OL,18,FMakerfield and Greater Manchester, and
OL,19,Fthe north of England, can fulfil their
OL,20,Fpotential.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
