SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781862536
OL,3,C'Final chance to change': Andy
OL,4,CBurnham's Makerfield victory speech in
OL,5,Cfull
OL,7,F"This result will bring about a
OL,8,Fcountry that works fairly for
OL,9,Feverywhere and for everybody.
OL,11,F"People here have voted for change.
OL,12,FThey have voted for more power for the
OL,13,FNorth and everywhere forgotten by
OL,14,FWestminster.
OL,16,F"They have voted for hope. Now, let's
OL,17,Fgive that back to them."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
